{"tid":831511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"譚志源：乘高鐵赴北京出席兩會會議　因為十分準時","createTime":"2018-09-22T04:24:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T11:40:18.000Z","uid":20933,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"580af98cfcde7d3c3bc5fd9e11268d0645fbd6ee","tid":831511,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T04:24:26.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】全國人大代表譚志源相信，市民對一地兩檢的顧慮會隨着高鐵開通而逐步消除，又稱明年會乘坐高鐵到北京出席兩會會議。<br />\n<br />\n全國人大代表譚志源：「我們和一眾港區人大已經開始討論明年三月上北京開會，是希望在香港乘高鐵上去，屆時看看安排怎樣，就算他們未必如此，我自己亦會乘高鐵上去。以往我做局長時在內地城市之間，我一定在有選擇情況下乘高鐵，因為十分準時，我的行程很緊密。」"},{"pid":"4b743b2ad83ebfeeaec148cfd4bd816baaba6e4e","tid":831511,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T04:24:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=321167&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D321167%26refer%3D&d=N4UaHsWRcl1wj2iks0eoosmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=564a6c30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D321167%26refer%3D&h=ab3ee852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=321167&amp;refer=</a>"},{"pid":"c04141be40b95648008264c468c2ae7cc9fe80dc","tid":831511,"uid":199211,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T04:33:11.000Z","msg":"高鐵八粒鐘 飛機兩個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做人做狗自己揀"},{"pid":"f3094a77df43423f11bcef3fd1d9cda840b544eb","tid":831511,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T04:48:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a07ab1f617cbe31bd102ce7d3e1f727696754196","tid":831511,"uid":33483,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T04:51:59.000Z","msg":"鳩up咋 有邊個唔識"},{"pid":"b061062bac0cda38b9184c415c0c6a7276fb7978","tid":831511,"uid":4575,"like